metadata.name: Blk Orchid ft. SOS Dynamikz-Weekend Love Visualizer #1/5
metadata.description:
2x Juno Award nominated producer and artist Blk Orchid and Grammy Winning Jamaican producer SOS Dynamikz team up for the high energy track. This is the culmination of 6 years of work on this record.

Collectors of the Weekend Love Visualizer will receive access to the exclusive Tellie site for $WKNDLOVE token holders which has exclusive video, lyrics and download to an exclusive song pack.

We plan to shoot a dope video for this song and proceeds of the sale of this collection will go towards flying SOS to Toronto, a place he has never been but wants to experience! it would be dope to finally meet and work in person on more BANGERS!


Thank you for your support of our music and art!


Weekend Love

Written by Renee Brown, Sheldon Sullivan and David Jackman  
Produced by Blk Orchid and SOS Dynamikz  
Mixed and Mastered by Austin Lee of Midnight Studios , Toronto  
Recorded and produced at home in Toronto (Orchid ) and Mandeville , JA (SOS)
